"textových záznamov."

#: ../../post_processing/metadata_editor.rst:438
msgid ""
"**Special Instructions**: this checkbox allows you to edit the editorial "
"usage instructions."
msgstr ""
"**Špeciálne pokyny**: toto zaškrtávacie políčko umožňuje upraviť redakčné "
"pokyny na použitie."

#: ../../post_processing/metadata_editor.rst:444
msgid "The XMP Status View from Edit Metadata Tool"
msgstr "Zobrazenie stavu XMP v nástroji Upraviť metadáta"

#: ../../post_processing/metadata_editor.rst:451
msgid ""
"**Language**: this checkbox allows you to select the languages used by the "
"content. Multiple text entries can be appended to the list."
msgstr ""
